Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.12,0:00:09.32,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.32,0:00:10.65,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Saitou speaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.65,0:00:12.53,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The new semester starts tomorrow.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.53,0:00:15.12,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When I heard the news of my brother's death,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.12,0:00:20.89,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I decided that I should use the remainder of the holiday to redeem myself.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.89,0:00:24.06,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I need to make up for the wrong I committed against her.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.06,0:00:29.74,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If only this nightmare were my only punishment.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.74,0:00:35.00,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That was just my stupid, selfish fantasy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.01,0:00:44.22,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fs32\pos(360,413)}Kuttskukiboshi{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.01,0:00:38.95,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs27}- Stars Intertwined -
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.95,0:00:44.22,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i0\fs27}Part Two{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.17,0:00:51.56,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,The strong, large-scale hurricane 11 appears to be approaching the Kanto coast.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.56,0:00:54.36,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Expect a large storm on the last weekend of summer vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.29,0:00:59.24,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She hasn't come...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.12,0:01:09.65,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,She brought it...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.15,0:01:31.03,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.91,0:01:42.68,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Location of your phone: PE shed
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.92,0:01:53.05,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,My phone's in the PE shed?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.29,0:01:59.47,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.14,0:02:45.64,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.64,0:02:48.18,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no! Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.25,0:02:55.59,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! What's going—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.65,0:03:10.20,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? What do you want...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.20,0:03:12.12,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.12,0:03:15.10,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it! {Ui: Suggestion, "Could you... stop it?!"}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.75,0:04:20.19,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Water.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.93,0:04:37.72,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not eating?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.83,0:04:49.77,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have some.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.62,0:05:29.81,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm... I think my hands are swollen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.01,0:05:39.40,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's done!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.40,0:05:42.68,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It should still work, even though I altered the shape.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.68,0:05:45.07,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This looks better.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.07,0:05:49.48,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This will make Kiichan want to carry it with her everyday.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.48,0:05:51.94,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Maybe...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.94,0:05:53.78,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is this weird?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.11,0:05:59.82,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Anyway, I won't tell her where I got it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.68,0:06:30.28,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,That was...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.70,0:06:44.11,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I've been at a friend's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.11,0:06:46.43,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.43,0:06:49.20,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,She invited me to come study with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.09,0:06:52.92,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.92,0:06:54.49,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.56,0:06:59.60,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,My parents are pissed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.64,0:07:02.62,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been several days.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.87,0:07:06.48,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you open that for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.01,0:07:09.89,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.99,0:07:29.87,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.87,0:07:33.60,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot the combination.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.29,0:07:37.69,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.69,0:07:40.46,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to ask you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.46,0:07:43.61,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What were you doing with your brother that time?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.69,0:07:47.42,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You still haven't told me anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.42,0:07:49.48,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Nothing much.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.48,0:07:52.40,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you hate me now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.40,0:07:53.55,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Just because of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.55,0:07:55.89,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,"Just that"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.47,0:08:00.73,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.61,0:08:15.21,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hot...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.21,0:08:20.54,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw before that the door to the pool changing rooms wasn't locked.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.54,0:08:23.13,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,When you're done, you don't need to close the door. {was: "When you're done using them, you don't need to close the door."}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.13,0:08:26.65,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, don't get me wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.65,0:08:31.22,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I was only with you because you found out about my powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.22,0:08:33.32,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm through with all this. {Hmmm... This is just a guess -- I think she said that she's fed up with all the experiments (noted in episode 1 and the next scene), so the right translation should be like "I'm through of all this."}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.43,0:08:36.31,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.99,0:08:49.46,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What have I been wanting to do this whole week?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.46,0:08:53.18,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm just a guinea pig in an experiment.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.18,0:08:58.15,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But... if I wanted to, I could always escape.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.15,0:09:06.71,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh, well... I'm just really angry right now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.35,0:09:18.50,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Incoming call: City General Hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.35,0:09:35.66,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so tan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.66,0:09:36.89,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I went to the beach four times!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.89,0:09:38.32,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.32,0:09:40.02,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, crap! The teacher's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.19,0:09:44.36,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, get to your seats! Homeroom is starting.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.46,0:09:47.37,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kawakami!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.37,0:09:50.51,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I marked you as absent since you weren't at the opening ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.51,0:09:52.32,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'll just mark you as late now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.32,0:09:54.20,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,So come on in.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.84,0:09:57.38,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wonder if it's 'cause of Saitou.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.38,0:10:02.10,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the first day of a new semester, and Kawakami's late, and Saitou's absent.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.10,0:10:04.44,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's start homeroom then!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.68,0:10:09.89,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Aaya didn't come to school.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.89,0:10:12.57,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wanted to ask how she felt,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.57,0:10:15.39,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but I couldn't bring myself to text or call her.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.12,0:10:19.37,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Maybe it's 'cause I'm scared that she wouldn't reply.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.37,0:10:21.21,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to forget everything,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.21,0:10:25.55,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and believe that maybe Saitou Aaya never existed in the first place.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.55,0:10:29.27,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But... I can't think that way.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.27,0:10:32.58,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My thoughts are only of her.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.16,0:10:36.06,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,And with that, I'll be collecting the summer break assignments now. {Ui: TLC CORRECTION! Not so much "Holiday" as "summer break". Haha. Wanted to act like Gott. XD}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.06,0:10:38.88,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring them in order of roll call.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.88,0:10:41.66,Main",,0287,0000,0000,,— {\i1}Assignment?{\i0}\N— Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.66,0:10:42.69,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I totally forgot...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.05,0:10:45.42,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.12,0:10:59.30,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.30,0:11:01.78,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Get home safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.32,0:12:05.27,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do it again, for the last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.51,0:12:09.21,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! My bag!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.43,0:12:29.56,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What the...? You're not wearing anyth—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.56,0:12:32.19,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to be embarrassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.19,0:12:35.20,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Just make your move.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.54,0:12:43.87,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.14,0:12:59.00,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... Why don't you have panties on, either?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.35,0:13:04.26,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't feel like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.09,0:13:08.59,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Your... finger...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.10,0:13:13.27,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.27,0:13:15.52,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me have yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.41,0:13:17.54,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.54,0:13:19.96,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.96,0:13:22.81,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is wrong, wrong, wrong, wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.83,0:13:28.30,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.30,0:13:32.80,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You seem even further gone than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.12,0:14:04.18,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,We could've gone in when there was more water in the tub.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.18,0:14:05.91,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Next, we'll do it in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.91,0:14:08.48,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no point anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.48,0:14:09.93,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, it's already...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.90,0:14:15.11,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I'm not even carrying it around now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.11,0:14:17.16,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't even know where it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.16,0:14:19.32,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't matter anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.32,0:14:21.34,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.84,0:14:27.10,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm leaving Japan tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.10,0:14:29.55,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, the experiment is finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.55,0:14:31.57,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep your secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.57,0:14:35.60,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,So let's make love tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.60,0:14:36.69,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,As many times as we can.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.39,0:14:41.13,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.28,0:14:55.23,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.35,0:14:59.43,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you the patient's sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.43,0:15:00.61,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...a hospital?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.61,0:15:02.88,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,We've had a look at the results,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.88,0:15:05.68,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,and unfortunately, there's been no improvement.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.68,0:15:10.00,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is partially due to the absence of cognitive symptoms that delayed diagnosis.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.00,0:15:12.64,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,And because it's so close to the spinal chord,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.64,0:15:14.79,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,surgical removal of the tumor will be extremely difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.79,0:15:16.33,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Saitou-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.29,0:15:18.03,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.03,0:15:20.19,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I am very sorry to say this,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.19,0:15:22.89,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,but the probability of success is extremely low.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.89,0:15:26.00,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Please be prepared for the worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.00,0:15:28.20,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,However, we will do our best.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.20,0:15:31.74,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, the surgery can be done this month,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.74,0:15:35.59,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,and then, the doctor said that you'll definitely get better!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.75,0:15:39.62,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I have no hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.62,0:15:40.92,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I just know it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.62,0:15:44.34,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.34,0:15:46.35,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe in yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.35,0:15:51.36,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't really help, but I'm praying that it'll be a success.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.51,0:15:54.33,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Praying won't change a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.81,0:15:54.32,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}In Operation
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.33,0:15:55.91,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.91,0:15:59.49,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,At least... before the end...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.49,0:16:01.39,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to make love with you before I die.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.87,0:16:04.55,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's always been on my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.55,0:16:08.13,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not just a sister to me anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.13,0:16:10.80,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you... talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.80,0:16:12.16,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.16,0:16:12.58,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.16,0:16:19.22,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry! There's something wrong with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.22,0:16:22.75,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it... I wasn't being serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.75,0:16:24.69,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to have the operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.69,0:16:27.87,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I don't do anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.87,0:16:33.77,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,So the reason why you've never dated anyone was...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.16,0:16:38.25,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.91,0:16:43.45,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You can do whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.63,0:16:48.66,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna do whatever I can to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.63,0:17:36.27,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}It'd be great if you could lock up before you leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.24,0:17:43.27,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.64,0:17:48.96,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I can lock up for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.66,0:18:02.36,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to tell me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.74,0:18:05.86,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.70,0:18:10.83,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.03,0:18:20.04,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.99,0:18:40.80,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.80,0:18:42.37,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.72,0:19:05.14,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you just disappear?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.44,0:19:09.14,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you explain everything to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.20,0:19:12.62,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Your brother died... Didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.51,0:19:18.39,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.44,0:19:26.14,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,And he manipulated his own little sister like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.14,0:19:30.10,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kiichan, did you see my memories?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.03,0:19:34.54,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,That was too selfish!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.54,0:19:36.30,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.30,0:19:39.02,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I didn't tell you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.02,0:19:41.13,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,But no matter what the reason was...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.13,0:19:44.65,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no changing the fact that I betrayed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.65,0:19:46.12,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's unforgivable.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.12,0:19:48.97,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. It {\i1}is{\i0} unforgivable.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.84,0:19:53.49,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you disappear again without telling me,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.42,0:19:56.87,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I really will kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.07,0:19:59.91,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Without tell—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.73,0:20:17.39,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.39,0:20:20.03,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll do more things together.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.39,0:20:23.27,Lyr,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The empress
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.03,0:20:21.97,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll fill each other with memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.97,0:20:23.27,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.27,0:20:26.68,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make you mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.27,0:20:28.04,Lyr,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}she stands all alone
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.68,0:20:30.85,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I have to force you with my powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.04,0:20:34.56,Lyr,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}with her forlorn
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.85,0:20:34.56,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Because no matter how you touch my body,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.56,0:20:39.18,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I get excited because I love you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.56,0:20:39.18,Lyr,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}blue jewels
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.18,0:20:41.66,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I'm just a pervert.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.18,0:20:45.92,Lyr,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}By your side,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.61,0:20:45.92,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.92,0:20:51.13,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what happens, I'll still like everything about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.92,0:20:51.47,Lyr,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I tremble
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.13,0:20:52.57,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.47,0:20:57.24,Lyr,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Just hold me
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.22,0:20:58.85,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is so messed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.24,0:21:02.74,Lyr,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}and my vanished courage
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.85,0:21:00.44,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,But... I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.51,0:21:04.93,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.74,0:21:07.04,Lyr,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There are many people
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.93,0:21:06.53,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Aaya...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.04,0:21:13.02,Lyr,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}searching for answers to this world
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.53,0:21:14.72,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot to lock the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.02,0:21:22.76,Lyr,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}but of you, I know nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.72,0:21:17.42,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.55,0:21:20.21,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.87,0:21:33.47,Lyr,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If only I could
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.15,0:21:32.31,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Aaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.20,0:21:35.75,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What should we do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.47,0:21:38.68,Lyr,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I would leave time behind
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.75,0:21:36.96,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,The sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.68,0:21:44.84,Lyr,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}and cry a yell that turns all ages to history
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.84,0:21:50.48,Lyr,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If only I could
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.48,0:21:55.39,Lyr,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}with the same passion
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.72,0:21:54.15,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to see the beautiful sea!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.39,0:22:01.13,Lyr,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll transform my naked figure
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.13,0:22:06.59,Lyr,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}into your only girlfriend
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.06,0:22:16.02,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I really have lost it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.02,0:22:18.35,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter. It's done its job.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.19,0:22:22.07,Lyr,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Infectiously
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.35,0:22:20.77,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you get that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.77,0:22:23.19,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I bought it online.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.07,0:22:26.96,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\pos(360,70)}When separated by a supernatural force ==>\NYour wish will come true in a new world
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.07,0:22:26.96,Lyr,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}an aurora in a bottle
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.19,0:22:26.13,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... You got it online...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.13,0:22:30.29,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,But... I'm glad I gave it a chance, {Ui: Sounds better than "tried to believe in it"}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.96,0:22:32.56,Lyr,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So exquisite
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.29,0:22:32.56,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,because I was able to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.56,0:22:36.13,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,And incredible things have happened! Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.56,0:22:38.10,Lyr,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A floating treasure
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.13,0:22:38.10,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.10,0:22:43.30,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but where are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.10,0:22:43.13,Lyr,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The universe
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.13,0:22:49.04,Lyr,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}roars a giant avalanche
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.30,0:22:46.27,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's a distant planet...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.27,0:22:48.01,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care where we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.01,0:22:50.44,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you're with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.04,0:22:59.01,Lyr,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}but I will not disappear
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.36,0:22:53.89,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Aaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.89,0:22:55.75,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I've seen the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.86,0:23:00.31,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be together forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.99,0:23:06.73,Lyr,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If we could
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.73,0:23:11.61,Lyr,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'd like you and I
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.61,0:23:17.96,Lyr,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}to share a kiss that would annihilate all reason
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.96,0:23:23.56,Lyr,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If I could
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.56,0:23:28.61,Lyr,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I would give flight to this passion
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.61,0:23:31.41,Lyr,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}as though they are ripples
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.41,0:23:40.63,Lyr,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I want to believe in these newborn feelings
